By: Zhuangzi
Locus:
  Chapter: 17
  Paragraph: 6
Title: Autumn Floods
---
\"Well then," said the Lord of the River, "if I recognize the hugeness
of heaven and earth and the smallness of the tip of a hair, will that
do?"
